        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Rural Investment in America Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Small Business Administration to make loans for certain costs to businesses that manufacture goods essential to critical infrastructure sectors in rural areas. Businesses that meet at least 75% of their job creation goals under such loans may receive partial loan forgiveness.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
